data.description: Wanting an affordable single family home? This is it! It has all the right stuff including the right price tag!! Completely remodeled including new roof, new tiled shower in MBA, stainless steel appliances, HWH, carpet, paint and more!!! All this on the end of the cul-de-sac make this cute home something special for your family! Lucky you! You just got a second chance on this home as its back on market due to no fault of the sellers.
